# Simple Currency App

This is a simple currency exchange app that allows users to convert currencies using the exchangerate API.

## Features

- Currency conversion based on real-time exchange rates
- User-friendly interface
- Easy-to-use API integration

## Usage

1. Enter the amount and select the source currency.
2. Choose the target currency.
3. Click on the "Convert" button to get the converted amount.

